#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Download Khan Academy
#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------


#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Software Requeriments:
#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    - python 3.x
    - get_flash_video 1.24


#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Using
#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

IMPORTANT: Before execute, copy the file indexFULL to index and delete all courses you don't want.

1 - ) Execute downloadkhanacademy.py 
2 - ) The program will open the file index and download the courses in there.

If one or more videos fail to download the script will retry to get them.



